data.title: ONDE VOCÊ MORA? (Lyrics in English)
data.meta_description: The Unrepeatable Love and Longing of 'Onde Você Mora?'. English translation: Love like yours / I will never have again / Love that I have never seen the same / That I will never see again / Love that is not asked for / Love that is
